KNBC 20.0 3. The Simpsons KTTV 18.8 4. Roseanne KABC 17.1 5. Frasier KNBC 17.0 
6. Wings KNBC 16.6 7. Home Improvement (8 p.m.) KABC 16.3 8. 60 Minutes KCBS 
16.1 9. Married ... With Children KTTV 15.6 10. Full House KABC 15.1 Weekly 
Averages 
</P>
