</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
102 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ATHLETE OF THE WEEK: GIRLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nicole Greathouse 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Buena 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Basketball 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Freshman 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: The 6-foot-2 post player has averaged 8.3 points and 7.0 
rebounds to complement Buena's other inside player, Arizona-bound senior Mikko 
Giordano. 
</P>
<P>
 WEEK AT A GLANCE: Giordano missed the Bulldogs' last two games because of a 
knee injury. Not to worry. Greathouse picked up the slack in those two games 
with 36 points, 20 rebounds and eight blocked shots. "She came in and did a 
good job for us," Coach Joe Vaughan said. "She offensive rebounds extremely 
well and shoots the ball real well between 12 and 15 feet." 
</P>
</TEXT>
