</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 State Assembly vote -- Because of an editing error, a story in an early 
edition of Tuesday's paper said 40 Assembly Republicans voted against 
increasing the penalty for carrying a concealed gun. The story should have said 
that 40 Republicans and Democrats rejected the measure. 
</P>
