 Fountain Valley 56, Huntington Beach 55 -- Lisa Feng's two free throws gave 
Fountain Valley a 56-52 lead with 12 seconds left. The Barons (16-6, 8-3) were 
led by Jen Ludwicki's game-high 18 points. Renee Kimoto had 16 points for 
Huntington Beach (7-14, 3-8). 
</P>
