<TEXT>
<P>
 Concordia moved into a tie for third place with an 82-81 victory over Westmont 
in a Golden State Athletic Conference men's basketball game Tuesday in Santa 
Barbara.  
</P>
<P>
 Craig Martin had 24 points and Travis Rousell and Darren Lax each had 13 
points for Concordia (14-8, 3-3).Lax made three of four three-point shots. 
</P>
