<P>
COMMUNITY COLLEGE ATHLETES OF THE WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Greg Vanden Ordel 
</P>
<P>
 Golden West, So. 
</P>
<P>
 Basketball / Center 
</P>
<P>
 Vanden Ordel, a Fountain Valley High graduate, had the most impressive week in 
his two-year career when he scored 48 points and added 25 rebounds in two 
losses for the Rustlers.Vanden Ordel, who is 6 feet 11, had 18 points on 
six-of-eight shooting from the field and 11 rebounds in a 94-80 loss to 
Fullerton Wednesday. He then made 12 of 13 shots from the field and finished 
with a career-high 30 points as Golden West lost to first-place Riverside, 
86-79. He is averaging 11 points, eight rebounds and three blocked shots this 
season. Other notables: 
