<DOCNO> LA020294-0265 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 009817 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 2, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
